  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bbe ? \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Was huge amount of money deposited in the bank accounts of the three vacated protesters? The truth is revealed!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been confirmed from the investigations of the CID that the reports of huge amount of money being sent from abroad to the bank accounts of the three eviction protesters are completely false.",
        "In the investigations carried out by the CID, it was confirmed that no large amount of money was ever deposited into their bank accounts either from abroad or from within and the Inspector General of Police has been notified in this regard.",
        "At the same time, the police said that the CIT had started investigations regarding the alleged deposit of Rs. Spokesperson Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Taltuva had informed this to Veerakesari.",
        "On the last 15th, there were reports on social media that the three foreign nationals had deposited 150 lakh rupees each into their newly opened bank accounts at the People's Bank - Union Place branch and within an hour of their depositing, they came in a white Prius motor vehicle and threatened the bank employee and took them away.",
        "Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Talduwa had already informed that investigations have been started in this regard.",
        "It has been confirmed from the investigations of the CID that the reports of large sums of money being sent from abroad to the bank accounts of the three Khalimaguthidal protesters are completely false.",
        "It is to be noted that in the investigations conducted by the CIDs, it was confirmed that large sums of money were never deposited into their bank accounts either from abroad or from within and the Inspector General of Police has been notified in this regard.",
        "At the same time, however, the three protestors had denied that they had received money through Union Place People's Bank Credit. It is noteworthy that they had also informed that they did not go to the bank branch on the given date as mentioned in the social networking site information."
      ],
